      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for avahi fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2025-68276: Fixed refuse to create wide-area record browsers when \n  wide-area is off (bsc#1256498)\n- CVE-2025-68471: Fixed DoS bug by changing assert to return (bsc#1256500)\n- CVE-2025-68468: Fixed DoS bug by removing incorrect assertion (bsc#1256499)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
